response.job_title: Mechatronics Engineer and IT Engineer - Senior Software Engineer
response.summary:
Mechatronics Engineer and IT Engineer from the National University of Colombia. 

I am interested in web, mobile, and desktop application development, IoT, robotics, and home automation. I have knowledge of Spring Boot, Java EE, Hibernate, JPA, SQL and NoSQL databases, GIT, Gradle, agile development methodologies, HTML, CSS, and handling services for serverless application development with AWS SAM. In the process of learning front-end software development tools and languages, as well as UIX. 

I am friendly, honest, responsible, multidisciplinary, dedicated, work well in teams, love learning new things, and experiencing new adventures.
response.skills: Desarrollo de software, Responsabilidad, Ética, Liderazgo, Comunicación interpersonal, Pensamiento crítico, Trabajo en equipo, Java, Amazon Web Services (AWS), SQL, NoSQL, Spring Framework, HTML, CSS, Metodologías ágiles, Desarrollo de aplicaciones

profile_positions.description: Ingeniero de desarrollo de software de aplicaciones web on premise y serverless utilizando herramientas como Java, bases de datos SQL y NoSQL, Gradle, Serverless Application Model, etc.
